cu.explanation_en: Setting GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_X2U to the same IP as GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_NG_AMF will cause IP address conflict and prevent X2-U interface establishment.
cu.explanation_zh: 將 GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_X2U 設定為與 GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_NG_AMF 相同的 IP 會導致 IP 地址衝突，並阻止 X2-U 接口建立。

du.explanation_en: Setting prach_msg1_FrequencyStart to -1, which is below the valid range (0 or positive), will cause PRACH frequency configuration failure and prevent random access.
du.explanation_zh: 將 prach_msg1_FrequencyStart 設定為 -1，低於有效範圍 (0 或正數)，會導致 PRACH 頻率配置失敗，並阻止隨機接入。
